---

<BaseLayout title="Driving School Software for UK ADIs | DVSA Tracking | DriveSchoolPro" description="Driving school software built for UK ADIs. Full DVSA 27-skills tracking, three-way scheduling with conflict detection, automated reminders, and pupil portal. From £22/month." image="/images/marketing/calendar-week-view.webp">
  <!-- Breadcrumbs with Schema -->
  <BreadcrumbsEnhanced
    site="driveschool"
    items={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'Driving School Software', href: '/driving-school-software/' }
    ]}
  />

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-navy to-gray-900 text-white py-16">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
      <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background-image: url('/images/hero-software.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container-custom relative">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <span class="badge-primary mb-4">Driving School Software</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Driving School Software That Works As Hard As You Do</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
          AI-generated lesson briefings. Full DVSA 8-category framework. Automated Google review requests. Stop juggling spreadsheets, WhatsApp, and paper diaries — DriveSchoolPro brings everything together in one platform.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href={OFFER.ctaPrimary.href} class="btn-primary text-lg px-8 py-4">{OFFER.ctaPrimary.label}</a>
          <a href="/pricing/" class="btn-secondary text-lg px-8 py-4">See Driving School Software Pricing</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Featured Answer -->
  <FeaturedAnswer question="What is driving school software?">
    Driving school software is a management platform for ADIs and driving schools that handles lesson scheduling, student progress tracking, test date management, invoicing, and instructor allocation. Modern platforms like DriveSchoolPro include a full DVSA competency framework with 27 skills across 8 categories, three-way conflict detection for scheduling, and automated email reminders that save instructors 10+ hours weekly.
  </FeaturedAnswer>

  <!-- Statistics Section -->
  <StatisticsSection
    site="driveschool"
    pageUrl="https://driveschoolpro.com/driving-school-software/"
    title="UK Driving School Industry Overview"
    stats={drivingStats}
  />

  <!-- What Is Driving School Software -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 id="what-is" class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">What Is Driving School Software?</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          <strong>Driving school software</strong> is a management platform that brings every part of running a driving school into one place — lesson scheduling, student progress, test tracking, invoicing, and instructor coordination. Instead of juggling a paper diary, a spreadsheet of payments, and WhatsApp threads with pupils, you work from a single system that any device can reach.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          For a UK ADI, good driving school software is built around the way you actually teach. It tracks each learner against the official DVSA framework of 27 skills, checks for booking clashes across student, instructor, and vehicle before they happen, and sends lesson reminders automatically so fewer pupils forget. The aim is simple: less time on admin in the evening, more time teaching — and a more professional experience for your students.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
          It replaces the patchwork most schools start with. Where a generic calendar app only knows about time, driving school software understands lessons, packages, pass rates, and compliance — so the tool works the way your business does rather than the other way around.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">Why Driving Schools Need Proper Software</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          You became a driving instructor to teach people to drive, not to spend evenings managing spreadsheets. But without the right tools, admin eats into your teaching time—and your income.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
          DriveSchoolPro handles the business side so you can focus on what you do best: helping students pass their tests.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-8">Core Features of Driving School Software</h2>
      </div>

      <!-- Full-width dashboard screenshot -->
